long_description: These car rack feet are designed with 8" of load bar clearance to accomodate high-dome roofs. Built to attach to cars with rain gutters. Provide a secure fit, even with narrow rain gutters. Protective surfaces on rack prevent sliding and protect car's paint. Require load bars, sold separately. Set includes 4 heavy-duty, lockable knobs. Thule's One Key lock cylinders are sold separately.
